        <listitem>
          <para>
            [Zeckmathederg] -	  
            Downgraded <envar>XORG_PREFIX</envar> to only be used for
            compatibility in BLFS as the Xorg stack is installed in
            <filename>/usr</filename>. This allows the Meson cross file
            to be used in the 32-bit installation of Mesa. Fixes issue
            <ulink url="&glfs-issues;/7">#7.</ulink>
          </para>
